snippet.title: Visual upgrade incoming for our indie game-Sausage vs. Vegetable(SVSV)
snippet.description:
We have a major update incoming for our indie title -Sausage vs. Vegetable(SVSV)! 
After 3 months of development since our last patch back in April, we are happy to share with you the latest trailer!
